  "text": ">what do you think about light meter apps?\nthey're shit, in even slightly difficult conditions (indoors, backlit, shade) they're less accurate than the meter on my 30 yo tlr\nwhenever i found myself with only a phone and color negative in a non-metered camera, i just use the manual mode of my phone's camera like a polaroid then convert the values for the camera and film",
  "board": "p",
  "date": "5/5/2018, 10:02:42 AM"
